Description: Playboy recognises his need to be in the limelight with Hollywood,The mass premium lends its redolent notes to his larger-than-life persona becoming a constant companion on screen and off. The Eau de Toilette combines the slightly floral, slightly zesty elements into a fragrance that will be scorched indelibly into your memory for a long time to come. Own the town and all its glamor with an attitude that never fails you and a fragrance that never dies out.Malibu Playboy fragrance's crisp aromatic scent evokes the energy of the ocean. It kicks off with the invigorating notes of tangy citrus, apple, mint, leafy green and verbena mixed with a spicy dash of distinctive neroli, creating a clean, light freshness. The fragrance builds to a floral heart of jasmine and iris with a touch of lemony coriander and smooth, woody cedar. Mellow undertones of musk, tonka, sandalwood and cashmere complete the sensation, delivering a heady mix of vibrancy and sensuality. Vegas Playboy fragrance echoes the Vegas guy's decadent, thrill seeking lifestyle. This oriental Fougere opens with the mouth watering head notes of apple, basil and tea, giving an immediate flash of freshness. An exquisite bouquet of lavender, jasmine and geranium at the heart creates a distinctive air of elegance. The woody, earthy base notes of musk, vanilla, tonka and georgywood add sensuous tones for a striking signature that's as dynamic and exciting as its inspiration

Title: Provogue Power Play Deodorant Spray  -  For Men, Women(150 ml)

The balance keeps shifting as they exchange one repartee after another and no resolution seems to be in sight. The electric aura is accentuated by the quick spice of Provogue Power Play Deo Spray, the fragrance of one who does not know how to give up. Made for both men and women, the mass premium deodorant spray characterizes strength of spirit and incites the never-back-down attitude within you. Compromising for anything less than the very best is out of question and the power play does not end - a seeming victory transcends into a defeat of sorts the very next day and vice versa. The liquid intensity of Power Play is packaged in a steel blue flacon with a robust black cap that highlights the unyielding nature of the fragrance and the one who it adorns.
